<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ص م د:</span> <span class="c2">(الصَّمَدُ)</span> السَّيِّدُ لِأَنَّهُ يُصْمَدُ إِلَيْهِ فِي الْحَوَائِجِ أَيْ يُقْصَدُ.<span class="c5"> يُقَالُ:</span> <span class="c2">(صَمَدَهُ)</span> مِنْ بَابِ نَصَرَ أَيْ قَصَدَهُ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>